articles.title: Asia suffers China blues; dollar hits 2023 top on yen - Reuters.com
articles.description: Asian shares struggled on Monday ahead of China data that is likely to amplify the case for serious stimulus even as Beijing seems deaf to the calls, while rising Treasury yields lifted the dollar to a 2023 peak on the embattled yen.
